headline: Cash App Afterpay Reveals Over 38% of U.S. Shoppers are Financially Stressed Amid Economic Pressures
summary: DISTRIBUTED-WORK-MODEL/OAKLAND, CA, September 11, 2025--Economic uncertainty isn’t going to see U.S. shoppers retreat from the holidays. On the contrary, new insights from Cash App Afterpay’s 2025 Holiday Survey gives an insight into how many Americans are determined to preserve seasonal traditions – and manage their stress – through mindful spending, planning ahead, and still finding a little time for self-care.
